# Forestry Syntax
This syntax was inspired by the nature all around us.

## Installing Localy
clone the repository with
```bash
$ git clone https://github.com/mishiki1002/forestry-syntax.git
```

Then you need to link the directory to atom.
```bash
$ apm link forestry-syntax
```

## Install Through atom
To do this you ned to type
```bash
apm install forestry-syntax
```
